<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mindfighter Hub | HSA Core</title>
    <style>
        :root { --neon-blue: #00f2ff; --deep-space: #0a0a12; --manga-white: #f5f5f5; }
        body { background-color: var(--deep-space); color: var(--manga-white); font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; margin: 0; overflow-x: hidden; }
        .hero { height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--neon-blue); position: relative; }
        .biometric-overlay { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 1px, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 1px, rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.05) 2px); pointer-events: none; }
        .btn-access { background: transparent; border: 2px solid var(--neon-blue); color: var(--neon-blue); padding: 15px 40px; font-size: 1.2rem; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.3); text-decoration: none; }
        .btn-access:hover { background: var(--neon-blue); color: var(--deep-space); box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--neon-blue); }
        .feature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; padding: 50px; background: #0e0e1a; }
        .card { border: 1px solid #222; padding: 25px; border-radius: 4px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .card:hover { border-color: var(--neon-blue); background: rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.02); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="biometric-overlay"></div>

<section class="hero">
    <h1 style="letter-spacing: 5px;">MINDFIGHTER HUB</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--neon-blue);">PROJECT: ADVENTURES OF THE MIND | HSA THREADS</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <a href="https://gemini.google.com/share/bf2f85858e1a" class="btn-access">Initialize Biometric Entry</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="feature-grid">
    <div class="card">
        <h3>Biometric NFT Framework</h3>
        <p>Encryption active. User identity linked via facial and iris recognition protocols.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>The Mangia Shell</h3>
        <p>Interface overlaying anime-style aesthetics with real-time data visualization.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>HSA Storybook Core</h3>
        <p>Direct access to the Threads of HSA narrative and geometric kaleidoscope perspective.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    // ANTIENTRYLOG PROTOCOL
    document.addEventListener('contextmenu', event => {
        event.preventDefault();
        alert("ANTIENTRYLOG: Unauthorized Biometric Access Attempt Detected. Security protocol engaged.");
    });
</script>

</body>
</html>
